    RTS
.L15B8
    LDA #&00
    STA player_missile_active
    RTS
.L15BE
    LDA #&00
    STA player_missile_active + 1
    RTS

.update_player_missiles
    LDA player_missile_step  \ Per-subframe ticker for the paired player missiles. RTS if `player_missile_step == 0` (idle). Phase 0: steps 1..4 spread the pair vertically (INC upper_y, DEC lower_y); phase 1: steps 5..7 advance the missile-frame index 1→2→3→4→5→2 (ping-pong loop) and walk the pair rightward by +1 px per subframe; phase 2: steps 8+ accelerate to +2 px/subframe. Each subframe re-plots whichever slots are active via `plot_player_missile`. When player_missile_x[0] >= &24 (off the right edge), erases both sprites with lev_erase_brush+&80 and resets the state (step = 0, x = 0). Note that the per-slot `player_missile_active` flag is cleared independently by `missile_hit_hazard` when a missile connects.
